    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-01-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-01-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="478"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d478">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Hovey</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 74.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-01-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 15, 1868.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I inclose for your information a copy of a
                        dispatch<note n="*" xml:id="d478fn1">For this inclosure see instruction No.
                        55, of the 15th of January, to the United States minister to Chili, p.
                        315.</note> which I have this day addressed to Judson Kilpatrick, esq.,
                    minister plenipotentiary, &amp;c., accredited by the United States near the
                    government of the republic of Chili, in relation to the mediation offered on
                    behalf of this government between the Queen of Spain and the allied republics of
                    South America.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvin P. Hovey</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
